在接受《每日经济新闻》记者采访时表示，当前智能驾驶的解决方案有很多，端到端的大模型纯视觉方案是新的方向，但它也有缺点，目前还不能断定它就是终极驾驶解决方案。https://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2024-12-05/3673366.html"},"attached_info":"CkAI2r7BkeeH90gQAxoJMTEyMTg0MDY2INa4xboGMAA45wRAFHIKNjAzNjc4MjM0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"19 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-385ba4c5a721c02dd8917d4b3deb196d_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1733498382.473632","card_id":"Q_659324300","target":{"id":659324300,"title":"为什么有这么多人买特斯拉？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/659324300","type":"question","created":1718774705,"answer_count":103,"follower_count":148,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3785,30747,35116,60628,70042],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"特斯拉在国内销量霸榜的原因是什么？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I2r7BkeeH90gQAxoJMTA4Nzk0MzE2ILHXybMGMAA4lAFAFXIJNjU5MzI0MzAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"18 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9cdabd09bf202c1395b7f1c7bb5d6ac3_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1733498382.473839","card_id":"Q_4623385505","target":{"id":4623385505,"title":"中国是制造业世界最大国，何时能够完全实现农业机械化现代化？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4623385505","type":"question","created":1732056696,"answer_count":82,"follower_count":170,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[465,22632,118616,212921],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI2r7BkeeH90gQAxoJMTExOTAxMzU3IPis9LkGMAA4qgFAFnIKNDYyMzM4NTUwNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"17 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":